Introducing Fort Wars, a new type of build battle! 

Fight over precious resources to upgrade your base and your equipment.

The team with the last fort standing will claim victory.

Tags: tycoon, building, survival, teams

Original Map Name: Fort Wars

Drop into Brite City, a huge open world adventure and earn reputation for team Shadow or Ghost!
Rank up and craft new loot as you explore Brite City. Break open vaults, complete bank heists, rent apartments and more!

Tags: open world, role playing, simulator teams

Original Map Name: Brite City Mafia

Prove your skill in this competitive mode! During each match, you'll earn Hype by either achieving high placements or eliminating opponents. As you gain Hype, you'll compete against tougher opponents with similar skill level.

Battle it out and put your skills to the test in the 4x5 Box Fight arena. First team to reach five round wins the Victory Royale.

Tags: 2v2, boxfight

Original Map Name: Pandvil Box Fights

Fight against other players in this unique FFA. Start off with a basic loadout which can be progressively upgraded as you eliminate your opponents!

Unlock abilities and special perks. Craft new items by searching materials around the map to gain an advantage.

Tags: battle, crafting, free for all, pvp

Cause Mayhem or prevent it in the Prison Breakout LTM by Echo

Be a Criminal and roam the city, rob stores, buy weapons and cause havoc, or be a Guard, prevent Prisoners from escaping and take down Criminals.
